# Floorplanner Static App: Grid, Snap, Dimensions, Walls, Doors, and Windows

## Overview

Upgrade the existing static lightweight floor-planning app into a more practical 2D floor-planning tool.

The app currently behaves mostly like a calibrated SVG shape editor. This spec adds the next set of floor-planning mechanics:

1. Grid overlay
2. Snap-to-grid
3. Selected-object dimension labels
4. Dimension-line annotations
5. Improved wall drawing
6. Doors and windows attached to walls

The implementation must preserve the existing lightweight static architecture.

